cross: Paphiopedilum Odette's Fantasy x Paphiopedilum Gyorgy Nagy

measurements.description: One flower on one 28.3-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal mucronate, light burgundy striated saturated-burgundy; synsepal burgundy, striated saturated-burgundy; petals ciliate, saturated burgundy, streaked light burgundy distally; pouch downy, black-burgundy; staminode green basally, light burgundy distally; substance hard; texture glossy.
